<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Add Product — Tesco Vegetable Expiry Tracker</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar', { page: 'add' }) %>

<main class="main-content">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div>
      <h1>➕ Add Stock Item</h1>
      <p>Record a new vegetable batch on the Tesco blockchain</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="form-layout">
    <div class="form-card">
      <form id="addProductForm">

        <div class="form-section-title">Product Information</div>
        <div class="form-row-2">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Tesco Product</label>
            <select id="productSelect" onchange="onProductSelect(this)">
              <option value="">— Select product —</option>
              <option value="Tesco Broccoli 500g|TSC-BRC-001|Brassica">🥦 Tesco Broccoli 500g</option>
              <option value="Tesco Baby Spinach 200g|TSC-SPN-002|Leafy">🥬 Tesco Baby Spinach 200g</option>
              <option value="Tesco Carrots 1kg|TSC-CAR-003|Root">🥕 Tesco Carrots 1kg</option>
              <option value="Tesco Red Peppers|TSC-PEP-004|Fruiting">🫑 Tesco Red Peppers</option>
              <option value="Tesco Courgettes|TSC-COU-005|Fruiting">🥒 Tesco Courgettes</option>
              <option value="Tesco Kale 200g|TSC-KAL-006|Leafy">🥬 Tesco Kale 200g</option>
              <option value="Tesco Leeks|TSC-LEE-007|Allium">🧅 Tesco Leeks</option>
              <option value="Tesco Cherry Tomatoes|TSC-TOM-008|Fruiting">🍅 Tesco Cherry Tomatoes</option>
              <option value="Tesco Sweet Potato|TSC-SWP-009|Root">🍠 Tesco Sweet Potato</option>
              <option value="Tesco Mushrooms 250g|TSC-MSH-010|Fungi">🍄 Tesco Mushrooms 250g</option>
              <option value="custom||">✏️ Custom Product…</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Category</label>
            <select id="category" required>
              <option value="">— Select —</option>
              <option value="Brassica">Brassica</option>
              <option value="Leafy">Leafy</option>
              <option value="Root">Root</option>
              <option value="Fruiting">Fruiting</option>
              <option value="Allium">Allium</option>
              <option value="Fungi">Fungi</option>
              <option value="Other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="customNameGroup" class="form-group hidden">
          <label>Custom Product Name *</label>
          <input type="text" id="productName" placeholder="e.g. Tesco Organic Beetroot"/>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row-2">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>SKU Code *</label>
            <input type="text" id="sku" placeholder="TSC-XXX-000" required/>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Supplier / Farm</label>
            <input type="text" id="supplier" placeholder="e.g. Kent Greens Ltd"/>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-section-title">💰 Supplier Payment</div>
        <div class="payment-notice">
          <div class="pn-icon">💸</div>
          <div>
            <div class="pn-title">Automatic ETH Payment</div>
            <div class="pn-desc">When this product is added, the smart contract will automatically send <strong>0.05 ETH</strong> to the supplier's wallet — instantly, trustlessly, on-chain.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Supplier Wallet Address</label>
          <input type="text" id="supplierWallet" placeholder="0x... paste a Ganache account address" style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.82rem;"/>
          <div class="field-hint">Paste any Ganache account address from MetaMask to receive payment</div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-section-title">Dates</div>
        <div class="form-row-3">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Harvest Date *</label>
            <input type="date" id="harvestDate" required/>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Packaging Date *</label>
            <input type="date" id="packagingDate" required/>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Expiry / Best Before *</label>
            <input type="date" id="expiryDate" required/>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Batch Number (optional)</label>
          <input type="text" id="batchNumber" placeholder="e.g. BATCH-2026-001"/>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" id="btnSubmit" class="btn-submit">🔗 Add Product to Blockchain</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="form-sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-payment">
        <div class="sidebar-title">💰 How Payments Work</div>
        <p>This works like Uber — when Tesco verifies a supplier's batch, the smart contract <strong>automatically releases ETH</strong> to the supplier wallet. No bank. No delay. Instant.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-card">
        <div class="sidebar-title">🔒 Immutable Record</div>
        <p>Each submission creates a permanent on-chain record that cannot be altered or deleted.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-card">
        <div class="sidebar-title">🦊 MetaMask Signing</div>
        <p>Connect MetaMask to sign transactions directly from your browser — a confirmation popup will appear.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ethers/5.7.2/ethers.umd.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/web3-utils.js"></script>
<script src="/js/add-product.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
